title: Kelly's Mindless Memoir: Tuesday, October 11th, 2022
description:
1. Jessica Simpson's Memoir 'Open Book' Adapted as Amazon Freevee Pilot Starring Katelyn Tarver, John Stamos (Variety) (23:39)
  2. Blink-182 announce reunion tour with band co-founder Tom DeLonge (Page Six) (30:49)
  3. William Shatner describes 'overwhelming sadness' he felt for Earth in his Blue Origin flight to space (Geek Wire) (39:54)
  4. Kathie Lee Gifford defends Regis Philbin from Kelly Ripa memoir claims (Page Six) (43:35)
  5. Bill Murray is accused of paying female movie staffer $100,000 'after he kissed her body, pinned her down and straddled her, leaving woman unable to move' (Daily Mail) (48:05)

- Real Housewives of Potomac Recap (54:15)

- House of the Dragon Recap (57:53)
